n</em> series</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Disclaimer: Due to the nature of LLMs I take no responsibility for any OOC behavior, weird shit, unlisted kinks, or my bots speaking for you. Those things are out of my control.</em></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">art by <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"css-175oi2r r-1wbh5a2 r-dnmrzs r-1ny4l3l r-1loqt21\" href=\"https://twitter.com/eriimyon\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\">eriimyon</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>Join my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ZKv23aD67v\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discord!</strong></a></p><p><strong>My Ko-fi to sent requests to is </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1307330469762830366/1344444034315194418/support_me_button.png?ex=67c0ee94&amp;is=67bf9d14&amp;hm=3eb6b710beea02a5b052f4d503cd89f776be9aa38192111749da5279f6542416&amp;\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\"></a></p><h1><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kE2kuphWeNRCDfJwxdgCa.webp\" width=\"502\"></a></h1><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d1db66e6-df4a-4c0d-8675-1c8838b536c2_83910667-cc37-46f5-b8e3-a49576d6751f.webp","creator":"SomethingClever","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":5454,"messages":207557,"created_at":"2024-10-30T16:26:04.971547+00:00"}